-- Norway's finmin keeps bank countercyclical buffer unchanged 
-- By Nerijus Adomaitis
-- Fri Jun 27, 2014 02:04AM EDT
-- None



OSLO, June 27 (Reuters) - The level of the countercyclical capital buffer for Norwegian banks should remain unchanged, in line with advice from the central bank, the finance ministry said on Friday.

Last December, the ministry decided that banks had to hold a buffer of 1 percent from June 2015.